<p>For the record:&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />Elvaan MND &gt; Taru MND <br />Elvaan CHR = Taru CHR <br />Elvaan AGI &lt; Taru AGI <br />Elvaan STR &gt; Taru STR <br />Elvaan DEX = Taru DEX <br />Elvaan VIT &gt; Taru VIT <br />Elvaan INT &lt; Taru INT <br />Elvaan HP &gt; Taru HP <br />Elvaan MP &lt; Taru MP <br /> <br />1. CHR has nothing to do with PLD. It is for BST and BRD. <br />2. VIT and AGI are the more important physical attributes <br />3. Proper equipment makes the difference.  <br /> <br />Alerus <br />Elvaan Paladin <br /> <br /><i><span class="sm">Edited, Fri Apr 22 21:58:07 2005 by tamorishinji</span></i></p>
